  "prompt": "How much money does a Ranji Trophy cricketer earn?",
  "response": "As of my last update, Ranji Trophy cricketers in India earn different amounts based on various factors, such as their experience, the state cricket association, and their performance. In general, players receive match fees for each game they participate in, and this can vary.\n\nFor the 2022-2023 season, match fees for players in the Ranji Trophy were approximately \u20b915,000 to \u20b950,000 per match, depending on their status and experience. Additionally, players may receive bonuses and other payments based on their contracts with their state associations and their performance in the tournament.\n\nIt's important to note that these figures can fluctuate from season to season, so for the most current and accurate information, it is advisable to check with the specific state cricket association or official announcements related to the Ranji Trophy.",
